<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .button {
            background-color: #4CAF50; /* Green */
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 4px 2px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .cancel-button {
            background-color: #f44336; /* Red */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Reservation Confirmation</h1>
    <p>Hi [Customer Name],</p>
    <p>Thank you for reserving your schedule with us.</p>

    <h3>Reservation Summary</h3>
    <p><strong>Date of Reservation:</strong> [Reservation Date]</p>
    <p><strong>Time Slot:</strong> [Time Slot]</p>
    <p><strong>Number of Guests:</strong> [Number of Guests]</p>
    <p><strong>Table Number:</strong> [Table Number]</p>
    <p><strong>Restaurant Branch:</strong> SM Fairview</p>

    <p>
        <a href="[CancelReservationLink]" class="button cancel-button">Cancel Reservation</a>
        <a href="[ModifyReservationLink]" class="button">Modify Reservation</a>
    </p>

    <p>We look forward to serving you!</p>
</body>
</html>
